than some of those kids, that's all.

18
00:02:25,436 --> 00:02:27,354
We just maybe have
less innocence than they do,

19
00:02:27,522 --> 00:02:29,242
but, I mean, I eat, I sleep,
I fall in love,

20
00:02:29,274 --> 00:02:30,774
