68
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,871
is to not be able
to do that anymore.

69
00:06:13,039 --> 00:06:14,998
If nothing comes up,
we would be in trouble.

70
00:06:15,166 --> 00:06:16,208
So far, so good.

